port said . `` i was happy i was able to regroup in the third set . physically i feel good . there are lots of positives i can take from it , especially beating a really good player and now being in the final . `` i want to be the one on the offensive and not the defensive , and that 's what i 'm going to try to do . `` i was trying to watch the first semifinal and see if that helped , but i play so much differently than julie ditty that it was hard to get anything from it . '' e-mail to a friend .
